"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["6y^{-1}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "6y^{-1}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "a4c9b8daa5bb54008409b43eabd445ff", "question_content": "**Rewrite the expression in the form $k\\cdot z^n$.**  \n*Write the exponent as an integer, fraction, or an exact decimal (not a mixed number).*\n\n$3\\sqrt[4] z\\cdot 3z{^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac34}}}=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["$\\begin{align}\n3\\sqrt[4] z\\cdot 3z{^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac34}}}&=3z^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}\\cdot 3z^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac34}}\n\\end{align}$", "$\\begin{align}\n3\\sqrt[4] z\\cdot 3z{^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac34}}}&=3z^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}\\cdot 3z^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac34}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=3\\cdot3\\cdot z^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14+\\dfrac34}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=9z^{1}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=9z\n\\end{align}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["9z", "9z^{1}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "9z"}, {"buttonSets": ["basic", "prealgebra"], "buttonsVisible": "focused", "considered": "correct", "form": false, "functions": ["f", "g", "h"], "key": 1, "linterContext": {"contentType": "", "highlightLint": false, "paths": [], "stack": []}, "simplify": false, "times": false, "value": "9z^{1}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "fdceca72cb4c51c3b7fbd908de5b4877", "question_content": "**Rewrite the expression in the form $k\\cdot z^n$.**  \n*Write the exponent as an integer, fraction, or an exact decimal (not a mixed number).*\n\n$\\dfrac{10\\sqrt[3]{z}}{2z^2}=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["$\\begin{align}\n\\dfrac{10\\sqrt[3]{z}}{2z^2}&=\\dfrac{10z^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac13}}}{2z^2}\n\\end{align}$", "$\\begin{align}\n\\dfrac{10\\sqrt[3]{z}}{2z^2}&=\\dfrac{10z^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac13}}}{2z^2}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=5\\cdot z\\^{\\frac{1}{3} - 2}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=5z\\^{-\\frac{5}{3}}\n\\end{align}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["5z^{-\\frac{5}{3}}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "5z^{-\\frac{5}{3}}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "eab24eb98dd159e0a922f2affde94039", "question_content": "**Rewrite the expression in the form $k\\cdot y^n$.**  \n*Write the exponent as an integer, fraction, or an exact decimal (not a mixed number).*\n\n$\\dfrac{8y^2}{2\\sqrt[4]y}=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["$\\begin{align}\n\\dfrac{8y^2}{2\\sqrt[4]y}&=\\dfrac{8y^2}{2y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}}\n\\end{align}$", "$\\begin{align}\n\\dfrac{8y^2}{2\\sqrt[4]y}&=\\dfrac{8y^2}{2y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=4\\cdot y\\^{2-\\frac{1}{4}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=4y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac74}}\n\\end{align}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["4y^{\\frac{7}{4}}", "4y^{1.75}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "4y^{\\frac{7}{4}}"}, {"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 1, "simplify": false, "value": "4y^{1.75}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "178d8ac8586e5725b8e45d22117b0a17", "question_content": "**Rewrite the expression in the form $k\\cdot x^n$.**  \n*Write the exponent as an integer, fraction, or an exact decimal (not a mixed number).*\n\n$\\dfrac{12\\sqrt x}{4x^3}=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["$\\begin{align}\n\\dfrac{12\\sqrt x}{4x^3}&=\\dfrac{12x^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac12}}}{4x^3}\n\\end{align}$", "$\\begin{align}\n\\dfrac{12\\sqrt x}{4x^3}&=\\dfrac{12x^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac12}}}{4x^3}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=3\\cdot x\\^{\\frac{1}{2} -3}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=3x\\^{-\\frac52}\n\\end{align}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["3x^{-\\frac{5}{2}}", "3x^{-2.5}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value"