on"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["3z^{\\frac{2}{9}}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "3z^{\\frac{2}{9}}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "7eb522fda55e5abc95fa1cb5f8236cd1", "question_content": "**Rewrite the expression in the form $k\\cdot x^n$.**  \n*Write the exponent as an integer, fraction, or an exact decimal (not a mixed number).*\n\n$\\left(16\\sqrt{x^3}\\right)^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["$\\begin{align}\n\\left(16\\sqrt{x^3}\\right)^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}&=\\left(16x^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac32}}\\right)^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}\n\\end{align}$", "$\\begin{align}\n\\left(16\\sqrt{x^3}\\right)^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}&=\\left(16x^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac32}}\\right)^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac14}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=16\\^{\\frac14} \\cdot x\\^{\\frac32\\cdot\\frac14}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=2x^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac38}}\n\\end{align}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["2x^{\\frac{3}{8}}", "2x^{0.375}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "2x^{\\frac{3}{8}}"}, {"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 1, "simplify": false, "value": "2x^{0.375}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "ae318141f3515d9d8c129b4f595ba944", "question_content": "**Rewrite the expression in the form $x^n$.**  \n*Write the exponent as an integer, fraction, or an exact decimal (not a mixed number).*\n\n$\\sqrt{x\\^{\\frac34}x\\^{-1}}=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["$\\begin{align}\n\\sqrt{x\\^{\\frac34}x\\^{-1}}&=\\sqrt{x\\^{\\frac34-1}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\sqrt{x\\^{\\frac14}}\n\\end{align}$", "$\\begin{align}\n\\sqrt{x\\^{\\frac34}x\\^{-1}}&=\\sqrt{x\\^{\\frac34-1}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\sqrt{x\\^{\\frac14}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\left(x\\^{-\\frac14}\\right)^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac12}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=x\\^{\\frac14\\cdot\\frac12}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=x\\^{-\\frac18}\n\\end{align}$"], "wid