rt[5]{z\\^{4-\\frac32}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\sqrt[5]{z^{^{\\scriptsize \\dfrac52}}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\left(z^{^{\\scriptsize \\dfrac52}}\\right)^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac15}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=z\\^{\\frac52\\cdot\\frac15}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=z^{^{\\scriptsize \\dfrac12}}\n\\end{align}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["z^{\\frac{1}{2}}", "z^{0.5}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "z^{\\frac{1}{2}}"}, {"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 1, "simplify": false, "value": "z^{0.5}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "b0509889028f5d0690d16fcfb724df83", "question_content": "**Rewrite the expression in the form $y^n$.**  \n*Write the exponent as an integer, fraction, or an exact decimal (not a mixed number).*\n\n$\\sqrt[3]{\\dfrac{y^2}{y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac45}}}}=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["$\\begin{align}\n\\sqrt[3]{\\dfrac{y^2}{y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac45}}}}&=\\sqrt[3]{y\\^{2-\\frac45}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\sqrt[3]{y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac65}}}\n\\end{align}$", "$\\begin{align}\n\\sqrt[3]{\\dfrac{y^2}{y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac45}}}}&=\\sqrt[3]{y\\^{2-\\frac45}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\sqrt[3]{y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac65}}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\left(y^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac65}}\\right)^{^{\\scriptsize\\dfrac13}}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=y\\^{\\frac65\\cdot\\frac13}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=y{^{^{\\scriptsize \\dfrac25}}}\n\\end{align}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["y^{\\frac{2}{5}}", "y^{0.4}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "y^{\\frac{2}{5}}"}, {"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 1, "simplify": false, "value": "y^{0.4}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "b0cb82dba5a3539bbdd9f9b333a3c8a7", "question_content": "**Rewrite the expression in the form $z^n$.**  \n*Write the exponent as an integer, fraction, or an exact decimal (not a mixed number).*\n\n$\\sqrt{\\dfrac{z}{z